source:
I am but a mere florist;
the dream flowers,
my children.

Do not mind her. It's not
that she hates <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var>;
she hates <var 1A 02 /var>everyone<var 1A 01 /var>.

This ain't somnus!
(Unless you're lookin'
for some somnus.)

Gobbie mindfruit is ripe
for bellyfilling! Here,
halflegs! Take a bite!
